law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 69, effective December 1, 1972. -- Amended 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 152, sec. 94, effective June 13, 1968. -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 34, sec. 1, effective June 16, 1960. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1482, 1596a-5, 1596a -8a, 1596a-9, 1596a-11.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: County board to issue certificates of election, certify votes.
